author: Lego_fan_
title: Detailed Keychain.
review: It is a nice little Keychain to hang from your keyring or your bag. I would not pay more then $5 for this I got it on Bricklink.com for $2.99.   I think the printing on this Item is incredible and looks true to Lord of the rings. The only thing is it is a little on the "kid friendly" side in terms of looks. Great on the whole and it got me some of my friends Old Lego collection for $20 for a basement full of it.
